    "### 1.7 Problem Decomposition\n",
    " \n",
    "#### Ultimate Impact Goal\n",
    " \n",
    "**\"Reduce individual carbon emissions across diverse population segments by replacing one-size-fits-all climate campaigns with data-driven, segment-specific interventions that target each group's dominant emission behaviours.\"**\n",
    " \n",
    "To reach this goal, we decompose the broad sustainability challenge into focused sub-problems using the 5W framework, then prioritise them by feasibility and impact."
   ]
